Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:16.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:00.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negative Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Captain Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why aren't you falling to your knees?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ghost clearly hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you counter it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything to counter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been negative!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The General Zombies Are Down in a Flash!!\NOars Feels Like an Adventure!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghosts' negative powers\Ndon't work on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a formidable human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Negative Hollow is ineffective?\NBut that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as a\Nhuman immune to that move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it...! I told them that\NI couldn't defeat the zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't they take out a single one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I defeat that woman,\Nit's obvious that they'll take me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! I'm gonna die like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless! No matter\Nhow I look at it, I'm doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have made some sort\Nof mistake a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to lose all will to\Nlive when they strike at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four times the negativity! Negative Hollows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them landed direct hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Thriller Bark got up and running,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one has been able to\Nstand up to those ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He out-negatived the Negative Ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumacy, sorry I'm always so mean to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effect has spread back to Perona-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that man a sage or a saint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen... When it comes to thinking negatively...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll have you know I'm unbeatable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He's super confident in a bad way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is it? For someone bursting\Nwith confidence, he looks mighty small.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he trying to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Busted!\N--Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crud! They saw through my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild Shot: Salt Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you! You've started to purify\Nmy darling Wild Zombies yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me! Salt Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got salt! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Covering your mouths is against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had kept that "Salt Star" part to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Usopp's\Nnegative outlook came in handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for him,\Nshe could have wiped us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got one terrifying ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey...\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where our paths diverge.\NI'm gonna head over to Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Be sure to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet! I'm the Will-o-the-wisp of Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He jumped...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this pretty high up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, supposedly an adrenaline rush\Ncan dull a person's sense of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to reach\Nthat mansion's top floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--That's where we'll find the skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you quite finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you be a man and admit defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a phoenix... Or perhaps a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have the strength left to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am just about ready to fully immobilize you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you will never come\Nafter your shadow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall I sever with my\Nspecial move, the Notch Slash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know a darn thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came from a certain kingdom's assault convoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The quick slash that I specialized in\Nwas called "Requiem La Banderole."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nickname my crewmates gave\Nthat technique out of admiration was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Three-Pace Hum: Notch Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may share my personality and abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want you to use that\Nname if you cannot remember
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my past and the feelings I harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel that you are\Nthe true master of this style,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,prove as much by defeating my "fake" style.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Pace Hum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Notch Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing them like this, they look just alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook's hair really resembles Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than anything,\NI want to apologize to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to apologize for my endless bad luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty years on the dark sea...\NTime has passed so slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe my life was in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lonesome... life it's been!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been so lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, where should I begin cutting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, this afro must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, this afro must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The mansion is shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why is the mansion shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd know! Maybe there's an earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Hey, Skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude! You took a royal beating,\Nbut you're still with us, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow this! You should\Nnot touch the loser in a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the legendary samurai who\Nsupposedly killed a dragon a long time ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on up there?\NThe whole place is shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship has probably gotten\Ncaught in a weird current.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's probably your fault, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want? What brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. You had some nerve,\Ntearing off my shadow earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking my shadow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right along with Zoro's, Sanji's, Brook's,\Nthe grandpa zombie's, and everyone's!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one greedy bastard!\NHow are you going to get them back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooch! Smooch! Smooch! Smooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooch! Smooch!\NSmooch! Smooch! Smooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooch! Smooch! Smooch!\NSmooch! Smooch! Smooch!...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second! Why is the ship shaking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't kiss my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Do you know what the deal is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our giant ship, Thriller Bark,\Nis caught in a strange current!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's changing our course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire island is shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like that Special Zombie\Nis messing with the rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving! It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move! Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Zombies, all of you are\Nto set out at once! Stop Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playtime is over, Special Zombie Oars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop him down from the legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Oars?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He vanished! Oars vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's so big...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he be so quick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm not made of rubber.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in the way of my adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilated?! But they just left...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right. They're as flat as pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They composed the strongest\Nzombie army on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were General Zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. They were out in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absurd... Wasn't Oars on our side...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he going on a rampage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies have no choice but to obey our orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to Thriller Bark\Nif we let him run loose...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's part of the Straw Hat Crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...! He pushed Ryuma back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a stinkin' aggressive pirate swordsman\Nwho practices the Three-Sword Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's damn strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your pride will stand for it,\NI bet he'd recover your shadow for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.75,0:22:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shadow? Really? Oh, please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!\NPlease recover my shadow for--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ploink!\N--Hey! Skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that looks like a good sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a good eye! This is in fact\None of the 21 O-Wazamono swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a black blade with a reversed saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This famous sword is called Shusui.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the sort of thing you see every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a sweet sword? Looks like\NI've come across a nice find!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I figured you'd have something\Nhalfway decent since you're a samurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll be using that sword from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.47,0:23:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ploink!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.37,0:23:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! I will never\Nleave your side ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Right! I will always be with you!\N--Bastard! We were in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, for all eternity!\N--of an important ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to listen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mincemeat is too good for the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blazing Knight Sanji!!\NKick Down the Fake Wedding!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
